OL,5,Cmemory dies
OL,7,FA grandad who set up a charity in
OL,8,Fmemory of his Manchester Arena victim
OL,9,Fgranddaughter has died.
OL,11,FOlivia Campbell-Hardy, 15, lost her
OL,12,Flife alongside 21 others, at the end
OL,13,Fof an Ariana Grande concert in May
OL,14,F2017.
OL,16,FHer grandfather, Steve Goodman, who
OL,17,FOlivia fondly called papa set up and
OL,18,Fspearheaded Liv's Trust - with the
OL,19,Fmotto "we choose love".
