OL,7,FThe Bury teenager wanted to become a
OL,8,Fsong and dance teacher and the
OL,9,Fcharity, which is also run by trustees
OL,10,Fand family and friends, promotes
OL,11,Fmusical education, dance, drama and
OL,12,Fthe arts across Greater Manchester.
OL,14,FScholarships have been funded and
OL,15,Fgrants handed out to help youngsters
OL,16,Fstudy and learn - all in Olivia's
OL,17,Fmemory.
