OL,7,FMr Goodman, from Radcliffe, Bury, died
OL,8,Fsuddenly on Monday 9 September, just
OL,9,Fdays after accepting an award on
OL,10,Fbehalf of the foundation and its aims.
OL,12,FIn a statement on Facebook, the
OL,13,Fcharity said: "It is with great
OL,14,Fsadness that we announce that on the
OL,15,F9th of September, suddenly, the
OL,16,Ffounder and chairman of the trust,
OL,17,FSteve, passed away.
OL,19,F"We ask that you celebrate Steve's
OL,20,Flife with love and fond memories as he
OL,21,Fwould not have wanted tears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
