OL,7,F"Steve's happiest times were
OL,8,Fsupporting the applicants of the trust
OL,9,Fand seeing them achieve their dreams.
OL,11,F"On Friday the 6th of September Steve,
OL,12,Fproudly accepted a BBC make a
OL,13,Fdifference award for bravery on behalf
OL,14,Fof the trust, which he spent all day
OL,15,Fin the shop showing everyone that came
OL,16,Fin. For Steve that award was a huge
OL,17,Fachievement and honour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
