OL,7,F"The words 'we choose love', again,
OL,8,Fring loudly for us. We ask that our
OL,9,Fprivacy is respected whilst we
OL,10,Fnavigate through this difficult time."
OL,12,FOlivia, a pupil at Tottington High
OL,13,FSchool, was one of the 22 to lose
OL,14,Ftheir lives in the Arena bombing of
OL,15,FMay 22, 2017.
OL,17,FLiv's Trust also has ties with the
OL,18,FRoyal Northern College of Music.
